OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779174391
OL,3,CFamily want answers after mobility
OL,4,Cscooter crash
OL,6,FThe family of a pensioner who was
OL,7,Finjured when a car hit her mobility
OL,8,Fscooter then drove off say they want
OL,9,Fto know why police have not caught the
OL,10,Fmotorist.
OL,12,FKumud Patel, who is 84, was left in
OL,13,Fthe road in Leicester after her
OL,14,Fmobility scooter was hit by a vehicle
OL,15,Fwhich stopped - then drove off - on
OL,16,FNovember 17 last year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779174391
OL,3,CFamily want answers after mobility
OL,4,Cscooter crash
OL,6,FWitnesses captured the car's
OL,7,Fregistration number and passed it on
OL,8,Fto police. Despite Mrs Patel suffering
OL,9,Fextensive injuries in the collision
OL,10,Falmost six months ago, no arrests have
OL,11,Fbeen made.
OL,13,FThe law said police have six months to
OL,14,Fstart a prosecution - which means time
OL,15,Fis running out if the family wants to
OL,16,Fsee the driver brought to justice.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779174391
OL,3,CFamily want answers after mobility
OL,4,Cscooter crash
OL,6,FMrs Patel had been crossing Victoria
OL,7,FPark Road on her way to the doctors
OL,8,Fwhen she was hit. She was left with a
OL,9,Fgash on her head, a broken rib and two
OL,10,Fmissing teeth.
OL,12,FShe now says she doesn't like to leave
OL,13,Fher home on the scooter. She had been
OL,14,Fan active member of her lcoal
OL,15,Fcommunity before being hit.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779174391
OL,3,CFamily want answers after mobility
OL,4,Cscooter crash
OL,6,FHer daughter, Asvina Brown said:
OL,7,F"There is a dangerous driver on the
OL,8,Froad, and that driver needs to be
OL,9,Fstopped because this has happened to
OL,10,Fmy mum but it could happen to somebody
OL,11,Felse and they get away with it.
OL,13,F"They should be off the road."
OL,15,FA number of people stopped to help her
OL,16,Fat the time, and took down the
OL,17,Fregistration number of the car.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779174391
OL,3,CFamily want answers after mobility
OL,4,Cscooter crash
OL,6,FMrs Patel's family say they are
OL,7,Fshocked the police have been unable to
OL,8,Ftrace the driver and bring them before
OL,9,Fthe court.
OL,11,FA Leicestershire Police spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "We received a call on 17
OL,13,FNovember last year regarding a non-
OL,14,Fstop collision in Leicester.
OL,16,F"It was reported that a mobility
OL,17,Fscooter had been involved in a
OL,18,Fcollision with a vehicle on Victoria
OL,19,FPark Road.
OL,26,@tD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779174391
OL,3,CFamily want answers after mobility
OL,4,Cscooter crash
OL,6,F"The driver of the car briefly stopped
OL,7,Fbefore leaving the scene.
OL,9,F"A woman in her 80s, was taken to
OL,10,Fhospital where she received treatment
OL,11,Ffor a broken rib, a small cut and
OL,12,Fdamage to several teeth.
OL,14,F"Officers attended the address of the
OL,15,Foffending vehicles registered keeper
OL,16,Fthat same evening but there was no
OL,17,Fanswer.
OL,19,F"Since then, a number of enquires have
OL,20,Fbeen carried out, and continue to be,
OL,21,Fto identify and locate the driver.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779174391
OL,3,CFamily want answers after mobility
OL,4,Cscooter crash
OL,6,F"These have included sending several
OL,7,Fnotices to the vehicles registered
OL,8,Fkeepers address including a further
OL,9,Faddress identified for them. These
OL,10,Faddresses have also been visited by
OL,11,Fofficers again with no response.
OL,13,F"A marker was placed on the vehicle to
OL,14,Fstop and question the driver should it
OL,15,Ftrigger an ANPR system. The offending
OL,16,Fvehicle now has a new registered
OL,17,Fkeeper, so a legal notice has been
OL,18,Fsent to the new keeper to try and
OL,19,Fascertain where and who they bought
OL,20,Fthe vehicle from.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779174391
OL,3,CFamily want answers after mobility
OL,4,Cscooter crash
OL,6,F"Attempts have been made to speak to a
OL,7,Fpossible witness who has yet to
OL,8,Frespond. A second possible witness has
OL,9,Fspoken to police but unfortunately did
OL,10,Fnot see the actual collision.
OL,12,F"Local CCTV and dashcam enquiries were
OL,13,Fcarried out and proved negative.
OL,14,FEnquiries with the vehicle's insurance
OL,15,Fdetails held at the time continue to
OL,16,Fbe progressed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779174391
OL,3,CFamily want answers after mobility
OL,4,Cscooter crash
OL,6,F"Our investigation is ongoing, and we
OL,7,Fare aware of and remain focused on,
OL,8,Fthe legal six-month time limit which
OL,9,Frequires the prosecution process to
OL,10,Fcommence within that timeframe.
OL,12,F"All potential lines of enquiry are
OL,13,Factively being investigated and the
OL,14,Fvictim's family is being kept
OL,15,Finformed."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
